title: Curry arrives for Port Shorts
text:
Stephen Curry has arrived in Cairns ahead of the 2015 Port Shorts Film Festival by: What are these? Stephen Curry arrivies at Cairns Airport ahead of the Port Shorts Film Festival. PICTURE: JUSTIN BRIERTY Source: News Limited 
AUSSIE comedian Stephen Curry and renowned producer Matt Hearn have arrived in Far North Queensland ahead of the 2015 Port Shorts Film Festival, beginning in Port Douglas tonight. 
The pair will be guest judges and mentors at the two-day event, which is celebrating its return after a seven-year hiatus. 
Curry, a Logie Award winning actor, said the standard of entries was “incredible”. 
“It’s amazing the amount of great storytellers and technicians on show,” he said. 
“Port Shorts is so good because everyone gets a forum to show their work.” 
About $15,000 in prizes is up for grabs at the 2015 Port Shorts.
